name: Engine
description: The engine is a power generator/power plant or a motor, which provides power to drive the automobile.

name: Battery
description: An automotive battery or car battery is a rechargeable battery that is used to start a motor vehicle.

name: Steering wheel
description: A steering wheel also called a driving wheel or a hand wheel is a type of steering control in vehicles.

name: Headlights
description: Car Headlights are one of the most essential parts of the car when driving down a dark and dingy road.

name: Fuel Gauge
description: Fuel gauge is an instrument used to indicate the amount of fuel in a fuel tank.

name: Brakes
description: Brake is a mechanical device that inhibits motion by absorbing energy from a moving system.
